config DC_HAPTIC_VIBRATOR
	tristate "SEC DC Haptic Vibrator"
	default n
	help
	  If you say yes here you will get support for the
	  SEC DC Vibrator. This will also support haptic
	  feedback with DC motor.

config USE_HAPTIC_DURATIONS
	tristate "SUPPORT haptic_durations node"
	default n
	help
	  If you say yes here you will use haptic duration interface
	  instead of haptic intensities interface.
	  In ONEUI 3.1 models, we will use haptic intensities interface,
	  and from ONEUI 3.5, we will use haptic duration interface

